<ul>
  <li>
    For this procedure, please use ECCS terminals installed on <a
      href="https://www.ecc.u-tokyo.ac.jp/announcement/2020/10/02_3224.html"
      >designated locations on campus (in Japanese)</a
    >.
  </li>
</ul>
<ol>
  <li>
    Please wait for an hour for the system to update after you have passed the
    "New User Information Seminar".
  </li>
  <li>Press the power button on the ECCS terminal to turn it on.</li>
  <li>
    In the log-in screen that appears, enter your UTokyo Account username
    (10-digit number) and password.
  </li>
</ol>
<ul>
  <li>
    If this procedure does not work, please consult the <a
      href="https://www.sodan.ecc.u-tokyo.ac.jp/about-us/tutors-working/"
      >ECCS tutors</a
    > (student staff) who are available at the main terminal locations.
  </li>
</ul>
